FBIS4-57224 "drlat094_j_94005" FBIS-LAT-94-094 Daily Report 14 May 1994 Panama President-Elect Names New Finance Minister President-Elect Names New Finance Minister PA1405165094 Panama City EL PANAMA AMERICA in Spanish 14 May 94 p A1 PA1405165094 Panama City EL PANAMA AMERICA Spanish BFN [Text] President-elect Ernesto Perez Balladares appointed Olmedo Miranda, Jr., to be the next finance and treasury minister. Miranda, who played a key role in promoting the Perez Balladares' candidacy during the political campaign, will take office on 1 September when the new government is installed. Olmedo Miranda, Jr. owns several businesses.
